  "segments": [
    {
      "id": "s001",
      "text": "Lesson 127.",
      "translation": {
        "text": "第127课。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s002",
      "text": "A Famous Actress.",
      "translation": {
        "text": "一位著名的女演员。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s003",
      "text": "Listen to the tape, then answer this question.",
      "translation": {
        "text": "听录音，然后回答这个问题。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s004",
      "text": "Who is only 29, and why is it so unclear?",
      "translation": {
        "text": "谁只有29岁？为什么这件事让人搞不清楚？"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s005",
      "text": "Can you recognize that woman, I think I can, It must be Karen Marsh, the actress.",
      "translation": {
        "text": "你能认出那个女人吗？我想我能。她一定是女演员卡伦·马什。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s006",
      "text": "I thought so.",
      "translation": {
        "text": "我也这么想。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s007",
      "text": "Who's that beside her?",
      "translation": {
        "text": "她旁边的那个人是谁？"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s008",
      "text": "That must be Conrad Reeves.",
      "translation": {
        "text": "那一定是康拉德·里夫斯。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s009",
      "text": "Conrad Reeves, the actor?",
      "translation": {
        "text": "演员康拉德·里夫斯？"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s010",
      "text": "It can't be.",
      "translation": {
        "text": "不可能。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s011",
      "text": "Let me have another look.",
      "translation": {
        "text": "让我再看一眼。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s012",
      "text": "I think you're right.",
      "translation": {
        "text": "我想你是对的。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s013",
      "text": "Isn't he her third husband?",
      "translation": {
        "text": "他不是她的第三任丈夫吗？"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s014",
      "text": "No.",
      "translation": {
        "text": "不是。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s015",
      "text": "He must be her fourth or fifth.",
      "translation": {
        "text": "他一定是她的第四任或第五任丈夫。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s016",
      "text": "Doesn't Karen Marsh look old?",
      "translation": {
        "text": "卡伦·马什看起来不是很老吗？"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s017",
      "text": "She does, doesn't she?",
      "translation": {
        "text": "是显老，对吧？"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s018",
      "text": "I read she's 29, but she must be at least 40.",
      "translation": {
        "text": "我看到报道说她29岁，但她肯定至少有40岁。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s019",
      "text": "I'm sure she is.",
      "translation": {
        "text": "我敢肯定她有。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s020",
      "text": "She was a famous actress when I was still at school.",
      "translation": {
        "text": "我还在上学时，她就已经是著名演员了。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s021",
      "text": "That was a long time ago, wasn't it?",
      "translation": {
        "text": "那是很久以前的事了，对吧？"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s022",
      "text": "Not that long ago.",
      "translation": {
        "text": "也没有那么久。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s023",
      "text": "I'm not more than 29 myself.",
      "translation": {
        "text": "我自己也还不到29岁呢。"
      }
    }
  ],
